<br>
[quote]Why, you might ask? Because say SoY and CB team up to kill PoP mobs, and keep their rotations seperate in the old world. They could just as easily join up into one guild, and be BotS-like in size. I assume that the don't want to. I also believe that its less about loot, and more about the different way that the guilds do things, and the personalities and play-styles of the peole within the guilds. Does that make sense?[/quote]<br>
<br>
Well, aside from all the issues, which I thought Rogg covered very well in his post, the above quote from Jeshter got me curious so I followed a link to SOY's website and counted up their members, which came out to 84.  Did the same for BotS and came up with 89 members.  Looks to me like SOY is already BotS-like in size without any help from CB.<br>
<br>
A lot of you are making the mistake of thinking uber == large.  Go to any of the uberguilds of EQ's website (FoH, AL, Triton, etc...) and you'll find most of them have less than 100 members.  The last part of Jeshter's quote, the personalities and play-styles of the people within the guilds, I think is what actually separates uberguilds from mid-lvl guilds among few other factors.<br>
<br>
I also find it humorous that leading upto Rogg's post, the &quot;demand&quot; was for further access to xp zones by being allowed to team up for 3 boss mobs that gives flags to zones which can also be quested into.  Now, it seems as though the &quot;demand&quot; has shifted to wanting to team up all the way upto RZ because none of them are on rotation so would not be violating any RTA rules per se, which is what the uberguilds &quot;claimed&quot; they were worried about and were lambasted for rampant paranoia.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jeshterdaggerfury>Jeshter Daggerfury</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Spin Doctor <br>
