If you don't want to subscribe to that idea, then I can see how you would think what you do.  But, in my scenerio, anything BEFORE PoP is irrelevant, and old rules apply.  New rules would be made for PoP mobs AND alliances.<br>
<br>
People can't possibly get the idea that we could do things DIFFERENT in this expansion IF WE WANT TO.  It's obvious though that we DO NOT WANT TO, and so I give up.<br>
<br>
Like I said....having thought it though, I think alliance would be to the detriment of both the guilds that ARE actually capable of the content and the alliances after they break up due to petty bickering. <p><P>
