<br>
The idea of making AD, Grummus, ect. rotation mobs still doesn't sit well with me.  However, I have an idea.<br>
<br>
Now I don't totally agree with my idea, but it's better than to have AD, Grummus, ect. as rotation mobs.  It's a lesser of two possible evils you might say.<br>
<br>
There are several mobs you have to kill to get flagged between, AD, Grummus, ect. and Rallos Zek the warlord.  Is it possible to make one of the mobs right before Rallos Zek a rotation?<br>
<br>
I'm not 100% familiar with the way PoP progression works, so forgive me if what I propose won't work.  But isn't the other Zek's required prior to killing Rallos Zek the Warlord?  What I mean is, can't we make Tallon or Vallon Zek a rotation?  That should protect the Rallos Zek rotation.  Then we only have 1 mob prior to Rallos Zek as a rotation instead of the 2 or 3 mobs proposed.<br>
<br>
The gains of this compromise are simple.  A lot of the PoP mobs remain FCFS since they are not contested.  Yet the Rallos Zek rotation is still protected in the same fashion.<br>
<br>
Hypothetically speaking,  as an added bonus to the anti-teaming people, the FCFS mobs like AD, Grummus, ect. can still become rotations in the future if they are contested.<br>
<br>
Off the top of my head, I see no reason why this compromise won't make people happy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ruldarswiftnote>Ruldar Swiftnote</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(4/24/03 1:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=646.topic&index=455>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Response to Teamwork thread in guild rep forum.</span><hr size=1> Wow, long thread.  I want back the hour and a half of my life I just spent reading this. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Oh well.<br>
